---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout title="Executive AI Workshops" description="AI workshops that end with decisions, not just inspiration. Half-day and full-day sessions for leadership teams.">

  <PageHero
    label="Services"
    title='AI workshops that end with <span class="text-ms-green-400">decisions</span>, not just inspiration.'
    subtitle="Most AI workshops leave executives impressed but paralyzed. Ours leave them with a prioritized action plan built on their actual business."
  />

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Your leadership team has sat through vendor demos. They've seen the ChatGPT magic tricks. Some are excited, some are skeptical, most are quietly unsure what to do next.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white font-medium">
        That gap between "AI is interesting" and "here's what we're doing Monday morning" is where companies lose months. Sometimes years.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What happens -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-16">What happens in a workshop.</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="bg-ms-dark-800 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Morning</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Understand</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-ms-green-400 mt-1">→</span>
              <span><strong class="text-white">AI landscape briefing: A guided tour of what's real, what's hype, and what matters for your industry. With live demonstrations on your actual use cases.</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-ms-green-400 mt-1">→</span>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Your company under the microscope: We map your processes, pain points, and data landscape together. Where is time being wasted? Where are decisions being made on gut feel?</strong></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-ms-dark-800 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Afternoon</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Decide</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-ms-green-400 mt-1">→</span>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Use case identification: 15-30 potential AI applications specific to your business. Grounded in your reality.</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-ms-green-400 mt-1">→</span>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Prioritization matrix: Every use case scored on business value, feasibility, and risk.</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-ms-green-400 mt-1">→</span>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Action roadmap: Who does what, by when, with what resources.</strong></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Deliverables -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">What you walk away with.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          "A prioritized use case shortlist (scored and ranked)",
          "A 90-day action plan with owners and milestones",
          "A shared vocabulary across your leadership team",
          "An honest assessment of your AI readiness, including strengths and gaps"
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ms-green-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">{item}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Format -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Format options.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-ms-dark-800 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Half-Day</h3>
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm mb-4">4 hours</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>Best for: Leadership alignment, quick assessment</li>
            <li>Group size: 5–15 executives</li>
            <li>Delivery: On-site or virtual</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-ms-dark-800 border border-ms-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Full-Day</h3>
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm mb-4">8 hours</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>Best for: Deep dive, use case development, full roadmap</li>
            <li>Group size: 8–20 executives + key staff</li>
            <li>Delivery: On-site recommended</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Not this -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">This is not</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gray-600">✕</span> A sales pitch for a specific AI tool</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gray-600">✕</span> A technical deep dive (though we go as deep as you want)</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gray-600">✕</span> A one-size-fits-all presentation</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-300">
        We prepare every workshop specifically for your company. We study your industry, your competitors, and your public data before we walk in. You'll notice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA buttonText="Book a Workshop" />

</Layout>
